the Dietary Guidelines for Americans, 1995</A><P>
<A HREF="http://www.faseb.org/ascn/">American Society of Clinical
Nutrition</A><P>
<A HREF="http://www.loop.com/~bkrentzman/index2.html">Archive of obesity
articles and information</A><P>
<HR>
</TD>
</TR>
</TABLE>
