  <BODY BACKGROUND="/gifs/fond.jpg">

      <TABLE BORDER=0 WIDTH="100%">
	<TR>
	  <TD>
	    <IMG WIDTH=102 SRC="gifs/ceo-logo.gif" ALT="CEO Logo">
	  <TD COLSPAN=1 ALIGN=CENTER>
	    <FONT SIZE="7">
	      CEO Experimental Demonstrator/Coastal Zone
	    </FONT>
	  </TD>
	  <TD>
	    <IMG ALIGN=MIDDLE SRC="/gifs/acri-small.gif" ALT="ACRI Logo">
	</TR>
	
	<TR>
	  <TD COLSPAN="3">	  
	    The scope of the Experimental Demonstrator is to capture user
	    requirements in the field of Coastal Zone. The work is performed
	    within the framework of a contract awarded by the European
	    Commission in preparation for the design and implementation
	    of the Centre for Earth Observation
	    (<A HREF="http://ceo-www.jrc.it:80/">CEO</A>).
	<TR>
	  <TD COLSPAN="3">
	    Your <A HREF="cz_interests.html">feedback</A> is therefore
	    important and will be considered in
	    the design of the future CEO concept.
	<TR>
	  <TD>
	  <TD COLSPAN="2">
	    <A HREF="cz_presentation.html" >
	      Background to CEO and Coastal Zone User Requirements Study</A>
	  <TD>
