<html>
  <body background = "/gifs/fond.jpg">
    <head>
      <title> ACRIPEL </title>
    </head>
      <H1> ACRIPEL System </H1>
      <h3> Dynamic wave absorber devices</h3>

      <h3><a href="/French/Recherche/Brevet/acripel.html"><img align=middle alt=french flag src="/gifs/FLAGFR.jpg">Cliquez ici pour lire la version francaise</a></h3>

      <img src="/gifs/bar_marbre_noir2.gif"><br><br>

      <H2> Function </h2>
      <big>
      <ul> Wave absorption mechanism for shoreline protection</ul>
    </big>

      <h2> Principle </h2>
      <big>
      <ul>
	  The system consists of a set of mobile tanks partly filled with water, attached to the seafloor by anchors or cables.<br><br>
	  The wave absorption is obtained by combining different hydrodynamic phenoma<br>
	  <ul>
	    <li> diffraction, radiation
	    <li> external energy dissipation as well as internal damping due to the motion induced by the waves on the structure
	  </ul>
      </ul>
    </big>

      <h2> Original aspects </h2>
      <big>
      <ul>
	<li> Tuning of wave absorption
	<li> Control of sediment transport
	<li> Low impact on environment
	<li> Preservation of alog-shore current
      </ul>
    </big>

      <h2> Application field </h2>
      <big>
      <ul>
	  Harbour beach protection<br>
	  Marinas<br>
	  Control of shoreline erosion<br>
	  Temporary protection of offshore sites
      </ul>
    </big>

      <h2> Patents</h2>
      <big>
      <ul>
	  patent ACRI - SETEC - ECOLE CENTRALE DE NANTES
      </ul>
    </big>

    </big>
      <P>
<IMG align=top src="/gifs/bar_marbre_noir2.gif">

