<DOCHDR>
http://acri.cica.fr:80/English/Products/SIMAC/simac.html 194.98.101.6 19970110085329 text/html 2679
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Fri, 10 Jan 1997 08:55:26 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
Content-type: text/html
Set-Cookie: Apache=widener6303852886526224; path=/
