<center>
<br>
<h2>Carbon Dioxide Mitigation Technologies</h2>
<p>
<img src="diox1.gif" WIDTH=450 HEIGHT=460 ALT="Large diagram of Mitigation Technologies"><p>
</center>
<p>
<hr size=4>
<font size=-1>
Web Implementation by Simon Newell,<a href="http://www.ibmpcug.co.uk/~djl/">DJL Software Consultancy Ltd.</a><br>
<i>Email - DJL@ibmpcug.co.uk, <a href="mailto:DJL@ibmpcug.co.uk">DJL@ibmpcug.co.uk</a></i>
