</html>


</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO>WT08-B04-227</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA092-000987-B017-145</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://acri.cica.fr:80/co2/diox-patent.html 194.98.101.6 19970110090236 text/html 10817
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
