<H1>MEDIAS Contact</H1>

Dr Podaire (MEDIAS France) is in charge of the collect and of the first
synthesis of the user requirements in Coastal Zone in France and more
precisely for activities related to remote sensing applications.
He also contributed to the identification of existing information 
network in coastal zones (national and european).

