<DOCHDR>
http://acri.cica.fr:80/co2/diox-home.html 194.98.101.6 19970110093229 text/html 7346
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Fri, 10 Jan 1997 09:34:18 GMT
Server: Apache/1.1.1
Content-type: text/html
